text: ohu ovunva bera gatte nam, ovun (veralata sendu vu) e avasthavedima asadharanaye bhumiyehi aparadha kirimata idiripat vannaha. minisune! obage akramikakam obatama napurata avasan vanu æta. (ebævin) melova jivitayehi podiyak suvaya vindiya hækiya. pasuva nam, apa vetama oba apasu emata sidu vanu æta. oba karamin sitiya dæya kumakda yanna e avasthavedi api obata dænum dennemu
